extends layout

block content
  .content
    h1 Buy  Cookies! 🍪🍪🍪
    p Although we have just one store and one recipe, Cookie Monster Inc! guarantees a sugar rush like none other! 
    
    
    p.notice-message Your bank might make you complete additional authentication steps and consent to this operation before proceeding.
    form(action='/submit-transaction', method='POST')
      if errorMessage
        p(class="error-message")=errorMessage
      p.message
        | How many 💸💸💸💸s worth of cookies would you like to buy ?
        | &nbsp;
        input(type='number', name='transaction_amount', step='any' value=transaction_amount)
        | &nbsp;
        input(type='submit', value='Proceed 🍪')

    p We will process the transaction with your <span style="font-size: 40px"> 🏦 </span>

